version_description: Wanted to try this with how I thought it could sound better and I think that the chords used sound brighter and make the guitar line more closely and subtly mimic the piano line when strummed to emphasize the 4th and 5th strings, as it sounds much better and has the brightness and tones of the original.

This one has chords for the entire song and each verse is slightly different. The other submissions only have one verse done and it leaves the reader to figure out the rest on their own. So I'm submitting a full version.
Key is different so you can sing even if you don't grow like the fray. But btw my intro is 100% correct and more easy.
